metadata.name: KOJ1 - The Traveller #1/7
metadata.description: Deep in the heart of the mystical realms, there resides a loyal fighter and elder of the Black Cat family, KOJ1. With the power to travel through time and space, KOJ1 embodied the values of his clan, displaying a wise and collected demeanor while battling fierce adversaries in elusive worlds and unknown dimensions. Despite the chaos that often threatens to engulf the universe, he remains resolute, keeping the balance between light and darkness.
